1
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:28,000
<font color="#fefefe">[Solemn instrumental music]</font>

2
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:30,500
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: Mr. Nolan, you said we could</font>
<font color="#fefefe">count on your loyalty.</font>

3
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,700
<i><font color="#fefefe">You didn't say you were coming</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to defend the Communist Party.</font></i>

4
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:40,400
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: We know they're out there, but</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be damned if I know how to find them.</font>

5
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:44,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">It'd be a lot easier on everybody...</font></i>

6
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:49,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">...if you all wore some identification,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">like a pin or a bumper sticker.</font></i>

7
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,800
<i><font color="#fefefe">Then we wouldn't have to go through this.</font></i>

8
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:54,700
<i><font color="#fefefe">Make it a lot easier on everybody, wouldn't it?</font></i>

9
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,100
<font color="#fefefe">I beg of you...</font>

10
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,700
<font color="#fefefe">...to please don't make me do this.</font>

11
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,800
<font color="#fefefe">Don't make me crawl through the mud.</font>

12
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:10,900
<font color="#fefefe">You know who they are.</font>

13
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,400
<font color="#fefefe">They're my friends.</font>

14
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:20,600
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: They are Communists.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Why do you feel they should be protected?</font>

15
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,700
<font color="#fefefe">We must protect America</font>
<font color="#fefefe">from the ideas they're spreading...</font>

16
00:02:24,100 --> 00:02:26,300
<font color="#fefefe">...through their films and television shows.</font>

17
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:30,300
<font color="#fefefe">When I joined the Party,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">they were trying to help people.</font>

18
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,400
<font color="#fefefe">I thought they were trying to help people.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">It was the Depression.</font>

19
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:38,300
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: People needed help.</font>

20
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,600
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: It was a good thing then.</font>

21
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:44,000
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: You came here and</font>
<font color="#fefefe">you confessed your membership.</font>

22
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:47,300
<font color="#fefefe">All we're asking you to do in good faith...</font>

23
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,500
<font color="#fefefe">...and to purge yourself</font>
<font color="#fefefe">of your mistakes in the past...</font>

24
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:53,500
<font color="#fefefe">...is to help us in identifying the people...</font>

25
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:55,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">...in those photographs.</font></i>

26
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:57,700
<font color="#fefefe">I don't want to be an informer.</font>

27
00:02:58,100 --> 00:03:02,700
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Real Americans have appeared</font>
<font color="#fefefe">before this Committee demonstrating loyalty.</font>

28
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:07,300
<font color="#fefefe">How do you think we got your name</font>
<font color="#fefefe">in the first place?</font>

29
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,100
<font color="#fefefe">I thought you were</font>
<font color="#fefefe">not a Communist anymore.</font>

30
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,300
<font color="#fefefe">I'm not! I told you!</font>

31
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,300
<font color="#fefefe">I think you're still a member.</font>

32
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:17,700
<font color="#fefefe">And I know some people</font>
<font color="#fefefe">who'd be interested to know that.</font>

33
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,600
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Would you speak up,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">please, son?</font>

34
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:23,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">There's nothing to be ashamed of here.</font></i>

35
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,200
<font color="#fefefe">[Train announcements]</font>

36
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,000
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: David! Over here!</font>

37
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,600
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Welcome back.</font>

38
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,600
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: What are you doing here?</font>

39
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,600
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Is this the hello</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I get after two months?</font>

40
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,900
<font color="#fefefe">-Feels like I just left. How are you?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-All right.</font>

41
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,600
<font color="#fefefe">You leave anything in France?</font>

42
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:11,200
<font color="#fefefe">-You don't have to buy everything you see.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Everything I can get my hands on.</font>

43
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,900
<font color="#fefefe">When I heard they sent a limo for you...</font>

44
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:18,900
<font color="#fefefe">...I decided this success has gone to your</font>
<font color="#fefefe">head. It's time we brought you down to earth.</font>

45
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,600
<font color="#fefefe">Thanks. So that's what friends are for?</font>

46
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:24,800
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: What's the news?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Did Lisa finally say yes?</font>

47
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:27,600
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Yes.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You're getting married?</font>

48
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,100
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You're not?</font>

49
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:33,200
<font color="#fefefe">She wouldn't swear to a loyalty oath,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">so it wasn't in my best interest to marry her.</font>

50
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:38,100
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: She swore all the time. She had</font>
<font color="#fefefe">a mouth like a sailor, drank like a fish.</font>

51
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: She wouldn't change?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Those things I liked.</font>

52
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,200
<font color="#fefefe">[Soft instrumental jazz]</font>

53
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:58,700
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Everything okay in town?</font>

54
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,000
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: This place is going crazy, David.</font>

55
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,800
<font color="#fefefe">I say we go back to France. Now.</font>

56
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,300
<font color="#fefefe">Not before I see Zanuck.</font>

57
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:09,000
<font color="#fefefe">What do we have to see Mr. Zanuck for?</font>

58
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:12,800
<font color="#fefefe">He wanted me back.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I guess to argue over casting and budgets.</font>

59
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,500
<font color="#fefefe">He'll give in.</font>

60
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:17,900
<font color="#fefefe">You can do no wrong around that guy.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I swear to God he loves you.</font>

61
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,500
<font color="#fefefe">Who loves me? God or Zanuck?</font>

62
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,400
<font color="#fefefe">It is hard to tell them apart sometimes.</font>

63
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,900
<font color="#fefefe">Seen Ruth?</font>

64
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:36,200
<font color="#fefefe">No, David, I haven't had any time.</font>

65
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">I'm doing some rewrites</font>
<font color="#fefefe">for my dear friend, Marilyn Monroe.</font></i>

66
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,300
<i><font color="#fefefe">And I feel kind of funny</font>
<font color="#fefefe">since you guys got divorced.</font></i>

67
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,800
<font color="#fefefe">I haven't had time to see anybody, honestly.</font>

68
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,600
<font color="#fefefe">How about you? Think you might see her?</font>

69
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,800
<font color="#fefefe">Who? Marilyn or Ruth?</font>

70
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,900
<font color="#fefefe">That's what I thought.</font>

71
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,900
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: They're here.</font>

72
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: They're here.</font>

73
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:12,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Everybody be quiet and say,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">''Surprise.'' Be ready!</font>

74
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:17,100
<font color="#fefefe">ALL: Surprise!</font>

75
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:23,800
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Sorry. I thought it was David.</font>

76
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:31,600
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Couldn't you wait for me, could you?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: You didn't say you'd be all day.</font>

77
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:34,100
<font color="#fefefe">I just wasn't going to miss this.</font>

78
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:35,400
<font color="#fefefe">No, of course not.</font>

79
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,100
<font color="#fefefe">You wouldn't miss seeing</font>
<font color="#fefefe">the great David Merrill.</font>

80
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:41,300
<font color="#fefefe">What is the matter with you? He's our friend.</font>

81
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,700
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Outside. Come on!</font>

82
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,500
<font color="#fefefe">What's going on?</font>

83
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:55,400
<font color="#fefefe">I surprised my own surprise party.</font>

84
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:58,300
<font color="#fefefe">Now I have to act like I like everyone.</font>

85
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:04,300
<font color="#fefefe">When you get settled down</font>
<font color="#fefefe">there's this idea I want to talk to you about.</font>

86
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Right now you want to talk?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Can't it wait till tomorrow?</font>

87
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,500
<font color="#fefefe">I want to go home.</font>

88
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:13,000
<font color="#fefefe">You're not doing this for me,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">you're doing it for yourself.</font>

89
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,700
<font color="#fefefe">Friends, Romans, Comrades!</font>

90
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,600
<font color="#fefefe">That got everyone's attention.</font>

91
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,300
<font color="#fefefe">We welcome back our friend David!</font>

92
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:25,100
<font color="#fefefe">Will you come on! Come on!</font>

93
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,400
<font color="#fefefe">Our friend.</font>

94
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:28,600
<font color="#fefefe">Larry?</font>

95
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,400
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: A brave man.</font>

96
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:34,600
<i><font color="#fefefe">Our friend, a brave man....</font></i>

97
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,100
<font color="#fefefe">Our friend...</font>

98
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:41,100
<font color="#fefefe">...who won't forget those of us</font>
<font color="#fefefe">who need work on his pictures.</font>

99
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,100
<font color="#fefefe">To my dear friend....</font>

100
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:52,800
<font color="#fefefe">What's your name again?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Bunny Baxter, who'll never work for me again.</font>

101
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:55,200
<font color="#fefefe">Just kidding.</font>

102
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:59,700
<font color="#fefefe">Thanks, everyone. It's a terrific welcome.</font>

103
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,900
<font color="#fefefe">I'm not surprised, but it's terrific.</font>

104
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,500
<font color="#fefefe">[Clapping]</font>

105
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:22,100
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: [Sings] ''Branded Un-American</font>

106
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:27,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">''Oh, there's a game called naming names</font></i>

107
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:31,200
<font color="#fefefe">''And let me tell you, gents and dames''</font>

108
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:34,200
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Two months</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and I get a hero's welcome.</font>

109
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:37,900
<font color="#fefefe">NELLY: Anyone brave enough</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to come back to this town is a hero.</font>

110
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,600
<font color="#fefefe">JOE: A great director, maybe, but a hero?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Never.</font>

111
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:45,100
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You part of this conspiracy?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">JOE: I deny it all. Hope your trip went bad.</font>

112
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:47,500
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: It went great.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">When can I see your movie?</font>

113
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:51,600
<font color="#fefefe">You have to buy a ticket like everyone else.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">That's if I figure out the ending.</font>

114
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:55,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You always have problems</font>
<font color="#fefefe">with endings. Want me to see it?</font>

115
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:58,200
<font color="#fefefe">I don't want your suggestions.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">How about Tuesday?</font>

116
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,500
<font color="#fefefe">JOE: It's good to see you. I've missed you.</font>

117
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,800
<font color="#fefefe">It's not easy times.</font>

118
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,500
<font color="#fefefe">Let's have a drink.</font>

119
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:15,200
<font color="#fefefe">Laugh!</font>

120
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,700
<font color="#fefefe">[Silence]</font>

121
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:20,200
<font color="#fefefe">Have a good time. Drink.</font>

122
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,900
<font color="#fefefe">Let's make it painless, right?</font>

123
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,500
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Who are we trying to kid?</font>

124
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,800
<font color="#fefefe">Everybody knows what's happening.</font>

125
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:33,400
<font color="#fefefe">I'm afraid to talk to my friends.</font>

126
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,600
<font color="#fefefe">My husband's crazy. We're all dead!</font>

127
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:40,700
<font color="#fefefe">-Dorothy, you all right?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Drink up! Don't let me spoil all your fun.</font>

128
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:42,300
<font color="#fefefe">Are you all right?</font>

129
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,400
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I have to go home.</font>

130
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:48,500
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Bunny, follow me to Dorothy's house.</font>

131
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,300
<font color="#fefefe">BERT: What's happening?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I'll be back.</font>

132
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,600
<font color="#fefefe">I don't want you driving.</font>

133
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,700
<font color="#fefefe">BERT: You've a 9:00 a.m.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">with Zanuck tomorrow.</font>

134
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:05,000
<font color="#fefefe">I got to see my kid. Can we make it 10:00?</font>

135
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,400
<font color="#fefefe">I don't think so. I can try.</font>

136
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,500
<font color="#fefefe">All right, shit. Leave it. I'll make it.</font>

137
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,900
<font color="#fefefe">BERT: Meet me at the Brown Derby after.</font>

138
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:27,500
<font color="#fefefe">[Foreboding instrumental music]</font>

139
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,600
<font color="#fefefe">Larry, what the hell are you doing?</font>

140
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,100
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Reorganizing my library.</font>

141
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:45,700
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Ever realize how book bindings are</font>
<font color="#fefefe">so well-made?</font>

142
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:50,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">The Catcher in the Rye, Tom Sawyer.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">All good books. What's the matter?</font></i>

143
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:52,700
<font color="#fefefe">Wait till Wood puts your nuts in a vise.</font>

144
00:10:53,700 --> 00:10:56,700
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Suddenly your taste</font>
<font color="#fefefe">in literature changes.</font>

145
00:10:57,100 --> 00:11:00,000
<font color="#fefefe">Everything changes, David. Real fast.</font>

146
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,700
<font color="#fefefe">Course, you don't have to worry.</font>

147
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:05,900
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: You're Zanuck's golden boy,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">aren't you?</font>

148
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,900
<font color="#fefefe">You're a brilliant man, David.</font>

149
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,700
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: A brilliant man.</font>

150
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:17,700
<font color="#fefefe">Good idea. James Joyce.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Can't write like him, burn him.</font>

151
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,900
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Ask him who he named today!</font>

152
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:24,000
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Ask him!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">LARRY: Don't listen to her. She's cracked!</font>

153
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,800
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: No, Matt. Go.</font>

154
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:30,500
<font color="#fefefe">How many of your friends did you sell out?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Did you name me?</font>

155
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">Did you name your son?</font></i>

156
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:37,400
<font color="#fefefe">-You could have hurt her!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-What am I going to do with her?</font>

157
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,100
<font color="#fefefe">The great actress!</font>

158
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:42,300
<font color="#fefefe">If you come here again, I'll kill you!</font>

159
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,600
<font color="#fefefe">What did you do?</font>

160
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:52,000
<font color="#fefefe">What any scared shitless,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">loyal American would have done.</font>

161
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,600
<font color="#fefefe">Welcome home, David.</font>

162
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:02,100
<font color="#fefefe">Welcome home.</font>

163
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:06,600
<font color="#fefefe">[Upbeat jazz song]</font>

164
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,900
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: Dad!</font>

165
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,300
<font color="#fefefe">[Car horn honks]</font>

166
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:29,700
<font color="#fefefe">You're back, Dad! You're back!</font>

167
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:34,800
<font color="#fefefe">You went across the street without checking</font>
<font color="#fefefe">the cars. What did I tell you about that?</font>

168
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You're getting so big.</font>

169
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,700
<font color="#fefefe">You're bigger than I am.</font>

170
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:43,200
<font color="#fefefe">You're way bigger than I am.</font>

171
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:47,300
<font color="#fefefe">-Are you taking me to school?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Tomorrow or the next day I will.</font>

172
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:50,200
<font color="#fefefe">Close your eyes and hold out your hands.</font>

173
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:55,600
<font color="#fefefe">A camera!</font>

174
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,600
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: It's neat, Dad. It's so neat.</font>

175
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,200
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: It's a very, very good....</font>

176
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:07,400
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: Can't you take me to school, Dad?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Please?</font>

177
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:10,900
<font color="#fefefe">Not today, pal.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I have a lot of important things I have to do.</font>

178
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:14,200
<font color="#fefefe">But tomorrow or the next day</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'll take you to school.</font>

179
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,400
<font color="#fefefe">Let's get you on the bus, young man.</font>

180
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,500
<font color="#fefefe">No talking to strangers.</font>

