00:53:47,300 --> 00:53:49,500
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: You're soaking.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: It's raining out.</font>

740
00:53:49,800 --> 00:53:53,400
<font color="#fefefe">I thought it might let up, but no such luck.</font>
