741
00:53:56,500 --> 00:53:58,400
<font color="#fefefe">Sit down. I'll get a towel.</font>

742
00:53:59,700 --> 00:54:01,000
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Nice place.</font>

743
00:54:06,900 --> 00:54:08,400
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I'll do it.</font>

744
00:54:08,700 --> 00:54:10,900
<font color="#fefefe">I always liked drying your hair.</font>

745
00:54:12,900 --> 00:54:14,600
<font color="#fefefe">You turning shy on me?</font>

746
00:54:16,500 --> 00:54:18,000
<font color="#fefefe">[Turns off TV]</font>

747
00:54:18,600 --> 00:54:20,200
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: Want a drink?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Sure.</font>

748
00:54:21,600 --> 00:54:23,800
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: Still drinking gin?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Gin's fine.</font>

749
00:54:24,500 --> 00:54:26,100
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: I picked up your habit.</font>

750
00:54:26,600 --> 00:54:28,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">I'll Join you.</font></i>

751
00:54:31,200 --> 00:54:32,600
<font color="#fefefe">Where's Abe?</font>

752
00:54:34,000 --> 00:54:37,400
<font color="#fefefe">In the country working</font>
<font color="#fefefe">on last minute rewrites.</font>

753
00:54:37,800 --> 00:54:39,500
<font color="#fefefe">He's gone for the weekend.</font>

754
00:54:43,100 --> 00:54:46,000
<font color="#fefefe">We thought we'd hear from you sooner.</font>

755
00:54:46,800 --> 00:54:49,700
<font color="#fefefe">I've been busy, seeing the sights.</font>

756
00:54:51,400 --> 00:54:54,600
<font color="#fefefe">I saw the Statue of Liberty,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">the new U.N. building.</font>

757
00:54:55,700 --> 00:54:57,300
<font color="#fefefe">It looks great.</font>

758
00:54:57,600 --> 00:55:01,200
<font color="#fefefe">You hate New York.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">And sightseeing? Come on.</font>

759
00:55:01,600 --> 00:55:03,600
<font color="#fefefe">If you're not doing a film here....</font>

760
00:55:04,100 --> 00:55:06,800
<font color="#fefefe">I'm not doing anything anywhere.</font>

761
00:55:08,500 --> 00:55:11,000
<font color="#fefefe">You never went three weeks without working.</font>

762
00:55:11,400 --> 00:55:13,800
<font color="#fefefe">You giving up your one and only love?</font>

763
00:55:14,900 --> 00:55:17,000
<font color="#fefefe">It's not by choice, I can tell you.</font>

764
00:55:19,000 --> 00:55:20,100
<font color="#fefefe">Why?</font>

765
00:55:22,300 --> 00:55:25,200
<font color="#fefefe">Because these guys follow me everywhere.</font>

766
00:55:25,500 --> 00:55:28,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">I feel like Joseph Cotton in The Third Man.</font></i>

767
00:55:28,700 --> 00:55:30,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: They must have better things to do.</font>

768
00:55:31,200 --> 00:55:32,500
<font color="#fefefe">Following you?</font>

769
00:55:37,400 --> 00:55:39,300
<font color="#fefefe">Did they follow you here?</font>

770
00:55:39,600 --> 00:55:40,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Might have.</font>

771
00:55:42,200 --> 00:55:44,900
<i><font color="#fefefe">They might be right outside your window.</font></i>

772
00:55:45,700 --> 00:55:48,800
<i><font color="#fefefe">Or in the neighbor's toilet listening to us.</font></i>

773
00:55:51,300 --> 00:55:53,800
<i><font color="#fefefe">You're smoking two cigarettes, Felicia.</font></i>

774
00:55:55,000 --> 00:55:56,800
<font color="#fefefe">You better go, honey.</font>

775
00:56:04,100 --> 00:56:06,900
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: And stay away from the theater.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Abe doesn't need problems.</font>

776
00:56:07,200 --> 00:56:09,100
<font color="#fefefe">They really got you, don't they?</font>

777
00:56:09,500 --> 00:56:12,700
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: Wait. You must need money.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">You always did.</font>

778
00:56:15,400 --> 00:56:18,400
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: I better not write you a check.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Take this.</font>

779
00:56:19,800 --> 00:56:20,800
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I don't want it.</font>

780
00:56:21,000 --> 00:56:22,700
<font color="#fefefe">Why not do what they want?</font>

781
00:56:23,100 --> 00:56:24,500
<font color="#fefefe">FELICIA: I'm surprised at you.</font>

782
00:56:24,800 --> 00:56:26,100
<font color="#fefefe">Don't be.</font>

783
00:56:26,600 --> 00:56:31,200
<font color="#fefefe">Maybe they asked in the wrong way,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">or maybe I don't like to be pushed.</font>

784
00:56:32,500 --> 00:56:36,600
<font color="#fefefe">Or maybe I'll just give them what they want.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'm sure tired of this shit.</font>

785
00:56:45,600 --> 00:56:47,000
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: Mr. Saltman, please.</font>

786
00:56:48,200 --> 00:56:50,700
<font color="#fefefe">I don't rent my equipment to amateurs.</font>

787
00:56:53,400 --> 00:56:56,400
<font color="#fefefe">Well, gentlemen, what can I do for the FBI?</font>

788
00:56:56,900 --> 00:57:00,900
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: Just a routine inquiry.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Does a David Merrill work here?</font>

789
00:57:01,500 --> 00:57:04,100
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: He's in the back</font>
<font color="#fefefe">working on equipment.</font>

790
00:57:04,400 --> 00:57:06,700
<i><font color="#fefefe">He fixes stuff. He's a good fixer.</font></i>

791
00:57:07,400 --> 00:57:09,200
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: How long has he worked here?</font>

792
00:57:09,500 --> 00:57:10,600
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: A few weeks.</font>

793
00:57:11,000 --> 00:57:13,500
<font color="#fefefe">He doesn't say much. Works hard.</font>

794
00:57:13,900 --> 00:57:14,800
<font color="#fefefe">What's wrong?</font>

795
00:57:15,200 --> 00:57:18,400
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: Did he commit a crime?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: Just a routine inquiry.</font>

796
00:57:18,900 --> 00:57:22,100
<font color="#fefefe">If and when he leaves this job,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">please let us know.</font>

797
00:57:24,200 --> 00:57:26,900
<font color="#fefefe">Just ask me if you want to know. Ask me.</font>

798
00:57:27,300 --> 00:57:30,000
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I'm right here. Ask me.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: Thank you, Mr. Saltman.</font>

799
00:57:30,200 --> 00:57:32,900
<font color="#fefefe">You want to know something,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">ask me, not him.</font>

800
00:57:33,200 --> 00:57:34,600
<font color="#fefefe">AGENT: Don't get upset.</font>

801
00:57:35,500 --> 00:57:38,100
<font color="#fefefe">Upset? Why should I be upset?</font>

802
00:57:38,600 --> 00:57:40,500
<font color="#fefefe">You've only ruined my life.</font>

803
00:57:40,700 --> 00:57:44,200
<font color="#fefefe">I'm right here.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">You have something to ask, ask me.</font>

804
00:57:44,600 --> 00:57:46,800
<font color="#fefefe">I'm warning you, I'm a federal officer.</font>

805
00:57:47,100 --> 00:57:48,500
<font color="#fefefe">Sam, let's go.</font>

806
00:57:48,800 --> 00:57:51,700
<font color="#fefefe">Sam? You're warning me? Go ahead, Sam.</font>

807
00:57:52,000 --> 00:57:54,200
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Warn me. How old are you, Sam?</font>

808
00:57:54,500 --> 00:57:56,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">Warn me.</font></i>

809
00:57:57,100 --> 00:58:00,400
<font color="#fefefe">Tell them I'm not going anywhere!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Understand?</font>

810
00:58:00,900 --> 00:58:03,200
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I'm not going anywhere! Right here.</font>

811
00:58:04,900 --> 00:58:08,200
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: They just wanted to know if--</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Now they know. I'm here.</font>

812
00:58:09,400 --> 00:58:10,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: They're after me, not you.</font>

813
00:58:12,300 --> 00:58:13,700
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: The FBI.</font>

814
00:58:14,100 --> 00:58:16,200
<font color="#fefefe">They make me nervous, David.</font>

815
00:58:25,700 --> 00:58:26,900
<font color="#fefefe">SALTMAN: Where you going?</font>

816
00:58:28,400 --> 00:58:31,700
<font color="#fefefe">Thank you. I appreciate</font>
<font color="#fefefe">everything you've done.</font>

817
00:58:50,900 --> 00:58:53,700
<font color="#fefefe">[Sorrowful instrumental music]</font>

818
00:59:19,600 --> 00:59:24,100
<font color="#fefefe">Operator? I want to make</font>
<font color="#fefefe">a long distance call to Los Angeles.</font>

819
00:59:24,800 --> 00:59:28,000
<font color="#fefefe">Collect. Crestview 0245.</font>

820
00:59:29,800 --> 00:59:31,900
<font color="#fefefe">Just say David's calling.</font>

821
00:59:40,800 --> 00:59:42,000
<font color="#fefefe">It's me.</font>

822
00:59:43,400 --> 00:59:45,000
<font color="#fefefe">How's the new place?</font>

823
01:00:35,400 --> 01:00:37,000
<font color="#fefefe">[Car horn honks]</font>

824
01:00:46,700 --> 01:00:49,800
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Sorry I'm late.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I had a meeting after school.</font>

825
01:00:50,400 --> 01:00:52,800
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: I am really sorry to be so late.</font>

826
01:00:53,200 --> 01:00:55,100
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: It's okay. It's good to see you.</font>

827
01:00:55,800 --> 01:00:57,200
<font color="#fefefe">Rough trip?</font>

828
01:00:57,400 --> 01:00:58,500
<font color="#fefefe">Long.</font>

829
01:00:59,600 --> 01:01:00,700
<font color="#fefefe">You want to drive?</font>

830
01:01:01,700 --> 01:01:03,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Where's Paulie?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: We're picking him up.</font>

831
01:01:04,100 --> 01:01:05,800
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: You always want to drive.</font>

832
01:01:08,800 --> 01:01:10,200
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You drive.</font>

833
01:01:10,500 --> 01:01:12,400
<font color="#fefefe">Will you be comfortable on the couch?</font>

834
01:01:12,700 --> 01:01:15,100
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be fine. Anything flat.</font>

835
01:01:16,900 --> 01:01:19,700
<font color="#fefefe">I know we said some things before you left.</font>

836
01:01:21,900 --> 01:01:24,600
<font color="#fefefe">Don't apologize. You were right.</font>

837
01:01:38,500 --> 01:01:40,700
<i><font color="#fefefe">TV: There's enough fresh air and sun...</font></i>

838
01:01:41,100 --> 01:01:44,400
<i><font color="#fefefe">...in this great country of ours for everybody.</font></i>

839
01:01:45,000 --> 01:01:47,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">And I'll see to it...</font></i>

840
01:01:47,400 --> 01:01:49,900
<i><font color="#fefefe">...that you get your share.</font></i>

841
01:02:00,700 --> 01:02:02,400
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Paulie, let Daddy sleep.</font>

842
01:02:02,900 --> 01:02:04,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">Five minutes, pal.</font></i>

843
01:02:05,500 --> 01:02:07,800
<font color="#fefefe">I got you now! I got you!</font>

844
01:02:08,900 --> 01:02:10,300
<font color="#fefefe">Dad, stop.</font>

845
01:02:20,500 --> 01:02:21,600
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: What are you doing?</font>

846
01:02:22,500 --> 01:02:24,900
<font color="#fefefe">Eat your breakfast. We have to go.</font>

847
01:02:28,000 --> 01:02:30,100
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Damn. I cannot get this.</font>

848
01:02:32,200 --> 01:02:33,400
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Where you going?</font>

849
01:02:34,300 --> 01:02:37,500
<font color="#fefefe">My 8:00 class. I can't get this necklace.</font>

850
01:02:43,600 --> 01:02:46,200
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Honey, are you finished?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: I'm hurrying.</font>

851
01:02:48,100 --> 01:02:49,600
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be late again.</font>

852
01:02:53,400 --> 01:02:55,100
<font color="#fefefe">David, don't, please.</font>

853
01:02:58,200 --> 01:03:00,100
<font color="#fefefe">Remember when I bought you this?</font>

854
01:03:00,900 --> 01:03:03,900
<font color="#fefefe">-It's a different one.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Than on our honeymoon?</font>

855
01:03:07,900 --> 01:03:09,800
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: I'm seeing Dorothy tonight.</font>

856
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:13,100
<font color="#fefefe">Paulie's staying at a friend's.</font>

857
01:03:15,000 --> 01:03:17,600
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: I'm taking her to a place in Malibu.</font>

858
01:03:18,000 --> 01:03:19,600
<font color="#fefefe">Can you afford that?</font>

859
01:03:20,800 --> 01:03:22,500
<font color="#fefefe">Can you believe you said that?</font>

860
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:24,400
<font color="#fefefe">I'd never say that.</font>

861
01:03:24,700 --> 01:03:25,800
<font color="#fefefe">Want to go?</font>

862
01:03:26,000 --> 01:03:27,500
<font color="#fefefe">Sure. You buying?</font>

863
01:03:30,400 --> 01:03:33,100
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Paulie, finished? We have to go.</font>

864
01:03:38,100 --> 01:03:39,400
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: Keys.</font>

865
01:03:40,200 --> 01:03:41,400
<font color="#fefefe">Don't mess up the bed.</font>

866
01:03:42,100 --> 01:03:43,700
<font color="#fefefe">It doesn't sag anymore.</font>

867
01:03:44,000 --> 01:03:45,400
<font color="#fefefe">Wonder why.</font>

868
01:03:46,000 --> 01:03:47,300
<font color="#fefefe">See you later.</font>

869
01:03:55,200 --> 01:03:57,100
<font color="#fefefe">[Soft jazz song]</font>

870
01:04:21,100 --> 01:04:22,600
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Dorothy, over here.</font>

871
01:04:26,400 --> 01:04:29,800
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I drove here so fast</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I thought I'd get a ticket.</font>

872
01:04:30,200 --> 01:04:34,600
<font color="#fefefe">This cop followed me for miles,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">but he never stopped me.</font>

873
01:04:35,900 --> 01:04:38,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: He just saw a beautiful blonde.</font>

874
01:04:38,600 --> 01:04:40,500
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: I love you as a blonde!</font>

875
01:04:40,900 --> 01:04:43,900
<font color="#fefefe">I've wanted to be a blonde for years.</font>

876
01:04:44,300 --> 01:04:46,700
<font color="#fefefe">The Joan Crawford look is so pass.</font>

877
01:04:47,000 --> 01:04:50,700
<font color="#fefefe">They want the Marilyn look.</font>
