878
01:04:51,100 --> 01:04:55,000
<font color="#fefefe">She must be sleeping with everyone in town</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to be so hot so fast.</font>

879
01:04:55,700 --> 01:04:59,800
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Bunny just finished a picture with her.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I doubt they slept together.</font>

880
01:05:01,600 --> 01:05:03,000
<font color="#fefefe">Can I get you a drink?</font>

881
01:05:03,500 --> 01:05:05,700
<font color="#fefefe">No. I've given the stuff up.</font>

882
01:05:06,300 --> 01:05:08,900
<font color="#fefefe">I've decided once and for all to stop drinking.</font>

883
01:05:09,500 --> 01:05:12,600
<font color="#fefefe">It's been the source of all my troubles.</font>

884
01:05:12,900 --> 01:05:15,000
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: It was killing me.</font>

885
01:05:15,300 --> 01:05:16,700
<font color="#fefefe">Just killing me.</font>

886
01:05:18,200 --> 01:05:20,500
<font color="#fefefe">I've decided to start working again.</font>

887
01:05:21,100 --> 01:05:23,400
<i><font color="#fefefe">I'm determined. I'm going to...</font></i>

888
01:05:23,900 --> 01:05:25,500
<font color="#fefefe">...get in control again.</font>

889
01:05:25,900 --> 01:05:28,500
<font color="#fefefe">Once I start working, I'll be okay.</font>

890
01:05:29,900 --> 01:05:31,200
<font color="#fefefe">You look great.</font>

891
01:05:36,000 --> 01:05:37,400
<font color="#fefefe">I'm really...</font>

892
01:05:38,600 --> 01:05:40,400
<font color="#fefefe">...very angry with you, David.</font>

893
01:05:41,800 --> 01:05:45,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: You know that</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I have wanted to do a Broadway play.</font>

894
01:05:45,700 --> 01:05:49,300
<font color="#fefefe">You went to New York</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and didn't even ask me to read your play.</font>

895
01:05:49,800 --> 01:05:52,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">If I can't depend on you,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">who can I depend on?</font></i>

896
01:05:52,900 --> 01:05:54,800
<font color="#fefefe">But I don't have a play.</font>

897
01:05:55,100 --> 01:05:59,200
<font color="#fefefe">I know that you just don't want anybody</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to know about it.</font>

898
01:05:59,700 --> 01:06:01,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">But listen to me, David.</font></i>

899
01:06:01,900 --> 01:06:06,200
<font color="#fefefe">Give me a part in your play.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'll get good reviews. And then....</font>

900
01:06:06,800 --> 01:06:09,900
<font color="#fefefe">Then how can Larry keep Matthew</font>
<font color="#fefefe">away from me?</font>

901
01:06:10,200 --> 01:06:14,200
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be the toast of Broadway</font>
<font color="#fefefe">in David's new play!</font>

902
01:06:14,900 --> 01:06:17,200
<font color="#fefefe">Listen. I don't have a play.</font>

903
01:06:17,600 --> 01:06:20,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Listen, Larry really is not that bad.</font>

904
01:06:20,800 --> 01:06:22,300
<font color="#fefefe">He really isn't.</font>

905
01:06:22,700 --> 01:06:25,700
<font color="#fefefe">We had a good life together.</font>

906
01:06:26,200 --> 01:06:28,000
<font color="#fefefe">A wonderful life.</font>

907
01:06:30,500 --> 01:06:32,500
<font color="#fefefe">Then all this stuff started.</font>

908
01:06:32,800 --> 01:06:34,600
<i><font color="#fefefe">It's not going to last.</font></i>

909
01:06:35,000 --> 01:06:36,500
<font color="#fefefe">I know that.</font>

910
01:06:36,700 --> 01:06:39,700
<font color="#fefefe">I know we'll get back together again.</font>

911
01:06:40,100 --> 01:06:42,300
<font color="#fefefe">Wouldn't that be great, Ruthie?</font>

912
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:45,400
<i><font color="#fefefe">Everything Just the way it was?</font></i>

913
01:06:45,900 --> 01:06:49,100
<font color="#fefefe">Me and Matty and Larry and....</font>

914
01:06:55,700 --> 01:06:59,300
<font color="#fefefe">That son of a bitch!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I haven't seen my baby in a month!</font>

915
01:06:59,700 --> 01:07:01,700
<font color="#fefefe">I don't know how he....</font>

916
01:07:02,100 --> 01:07:03,600
<font color="#fefefe">Let's get you home.</font>

917
01:07:04,400 --> 01:07:07,300
<font color="#fefefe">You're always right. I should be at home.</font>

918
01:07:07,500 --> 01:07:11,400
<font color="#fefefe">What if Larry tries to call me</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and wants to bring Matthew home?</font>

919
01:07:13,700 --> 01:07:15,700
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I've got to get home.</font>

920
01:07:16,200 --> 01:07:20,600
<font color="#fefefe">I have to pick up a new Christmas tree</font>
<font color="#fefefe">because Matthew loves Christmas.</font>

921
01:07:26,900 --> 01:07:29,700
<font color="#fefefe">I bet Larry and Matt are waiting for me.</font>

922
01:07:30,100 --> 01:07:33,300
<font color="#fefefe">I have to hurry. They're both waiting for me.</font>

923
01:07:33,700 --> 01:07:35,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I have to see my baby.</font>

924
01:07:39,400 --> 01:07:41,200
<font color="#fefefe">-Are you all right?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Fine.</font>

925
01:07:41,500 --> 01:07:44,000
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: I just want to go home. I'm sure.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Sure?</font>

926
01:07:47,000 --> 01:07:48,100
<font color="#fefefe">You okay?</font>

927
01:07:48,400 --> 01:07:49,400
<font color="#fefefe">Please.</font>

928
01:07:51,100 --> 01:07:52,400
<font color="#fefefe">I'm okay.</font>

929
01:07:56,300 --> 01:07:57,300
<font color="#fefefe">DOROTHY: Please.</font>

930
01:07:59,000 --> 01:08:00,300
<font color="#fefefe">All right.</font>

931
01:08:00,600 --> 01:08:01,800
<font color="#fefefe">I'm okay.</font>

932
01:08:24,900 --> 01:08:27,700
<font color="#fefefe">[Dramatic instrumental music]</font>

933
01:08:38,400 --> 01:08:40,700
<font color="#fefefe">[Soft instrumental music]</font>

934
01:08:43,000 --> 01:08:45,300
<font color="#fefefe">[Priest recites burial service]</font>

935
01:08:59,400 --> 01:09:04,100
<font color="#fefefe">PRIEST: May her soul,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">through the mercy of God, rest in peace.</font>

936
01:09:13,200 --> 01:09:15,800
<font color="#fefefe">[Soft instrumental music continues]</font>

937
01:10:10,600 --> 01:10:12,400
<font color="#fefefe">[Phone rings]</font>

938
01:10:19,600 --> 01:10:20,500
<font color="#fefefe">Bert?</font>

939
01:10:30,200 --> 01:10:31,900
<font color="#fefefe">Will you handle the deal?</font>

940
01:10:36,700 --> 01:10:38,300
<font color="#fefefe">Thanks, thanks.</font>

941
01:10:44,000 --> 01:10:47,400
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I think I got a job. Gower Studios.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Bert just called.</font>

942
01:10:47,900 --> 01:10:50,600
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: What picture?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: A producer named Gene Woods.</font>

943
01:10:50,900 --> 01:10:55,100
<font color="#fefefe">He's a half-assed producer.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">But it might be good. I'll call you later.</font>

944
01:10:57,700 --> 01:11:01,000
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: I knew we'd work together.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">You didn't believe me.</font>

945
01:11:01,400 --> 01:11:04,100
<font color="#fefefe">-I believe you.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-Monogram gave me seven days for this.</font>

946
01:11:04,400 --> 01:11:08,200
<font color="#fefefe">They brought me in to give it style.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">And that's why you're here.</font>

947
01:11:08,700 --> 01:11:11,900
<font color="#fefefe">-What happened to the director?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-He took a flop.</font>

948
01:11:12,100 --> 01:11:15,400
<font color="#fefefe">I have to look at the script.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I need time to prepare.</font>

949
01:11:15,800 --> 01:11:19,700
<font color="#fefefe">No time. Don't worry, the actors are mints.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Here's the script.</font>

950
01:11:20,000 --> 01:11:24,200
<font color="#fefefe">This scene is next. Take a nice lunch,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">a half-hour, and read the rest.</font>

951
01:11:24,600 --> 01:11:27,200
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be in my office. Don't worry.</font>

952
01:11:27,500 --> 01:11:31,600
<font color="#fefefe">We'll walk down the aisle together.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'll see you at the Oscars.</font>

953
01:11:32,100 --> 01:11:33,900
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: I'm in my office if you need me.</font>

954
01:11:45,700 --> 01:11:48,400
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Who's the 1st A.D.?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">JACK: I am. Jack.</font>

955
01:11:52,400 --> 01:11:54,600
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: You're the sheriff?. Good to meet you.</font>

956
01:11:55,200 --> 01:11:57,400
<font color="#fefefe">-What's the next setup?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-The villains ride in.</font>

957
01:11:57,600 --> 01:11:59,900
<font color="#fefefe">Tie the horses in front of the saloon.</font>

958
01:12:00,100 --> 01:12:02,500
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: They start a fight?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">JACK: Eventually.</font>

959
01:12:04,300 --> 01:12:07,500
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: What's your first line?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">JERRY: ''Frank Miller. Good to see you.''</font>

960
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:10,100
<font color="#fefefe">-Got a dolly with an arm?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-We can fix something.</font>

961
01:12:10,400 --> 01:12:12,800
<font color="#fefefe">We'll start tight on....</font>

962
01:12:14,700 --> 01:12:18,700
<font color="#fefefe">We'll start on Jerry then pull back</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to bring in the bad guys.</font>

963
01:12:19,300 --> 01:12:22,100
<font color="#fefefe">Jerry comes out, sees them, goes back in.</font>

964
01:12:22,500 --> 01:12:25,300
<font color="#fefefe">The bad guys go in, then the shit hits the fan.</font>

965
01:12:25,600 --> 01:12:27,900
<font color="#fefefe">Then the bad guys come flying out.</font>

966
01:12:28,300 --> 01:12:31,500
<font color="#fefefe">Here, face down.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Then Jerry walks out and says:</font>

967
01:12:32,800 --> 01:12:34,700
<font color="#fefefe">''Frank Miller. Good to see you.''</font>

968
01:12:35,000 --> 01:12:36,700
<font color="#fefefe">One shot. That's it.</font>

969
01:12:37,000 --> 01:12:38,900
<font color="#fefefe">-It's not in the script.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-It is now.</font>

970
01:13:14,700 --> 01:13:15,700
<font color="#fefefe">What's up?</font>

971
01:13:16,400 --> 01:13:18,300
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: Fractions.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Let me see.</font>

972
01:13:21,400 --> 01:13:22,700
<font color="#fefefe">''One over two....''</font>

973
01:13:23,000 --> 01:13:24,800
<font color="#fefefe">-Daddy's working.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-I sure am.</font>

974
01:13:25,200 --> 01:13:27,500
<font color="#fefefe">I hated fractions. Got a D.</font>

975
01:13:27,900 --> 01:13:29,600
<font color="#fefefe">You never told me that.</font>

976
01:13:29,900 --> 01:13:31,200
<font color="#fefefe">I sure did.</font>

977
01:13:32,400 --> 01:13:33,900
<font color="#fefefe">Only one or two.</font>

978
01:13:36,200 --> 01:13:37,800
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: ''One over two...</font>

979
01:13:38,400 --> 01:13:41,700
<font color="#fefefe">''...is less than or greater than...</font>

980
01:13:42,300 --> 01:13:43,800
<font color="#fefefe">''...one over one?''</font>

981
01:13:48,000 --> 01:13:49,400
<font color="#fefefe">What do you think?</font>

982
01:14:13,000 --> 01:14:15,000
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Cut. That's a take.</font>

983
01:14:17,300 --> 01:14:18,900
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: David, I must talk to you.</font>

984
01:14:19,300 --> 01:14:22,300
<font color="#fefefe">I got 40 days to shoot and six days to do it.</font>

985
01:14:22,600 --> 01:14:25,900
<font color="#fefefe">It doesn't matter.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Norman here is taking over.</font>

986
01:14:27,800 --> 01:14:29,700
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: What?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: Monogram balked on me.</font>

987
01:14:30,000 --> 01:14:33,300
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: The projectionists won't run a movie</font>
<font color="#fefefe">made by a Commie.</font>

988
01:14:33,800 --> 01:14:36,400
<font color="#fefefe">Then they're Commies.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Ridiculous. Norman....</font>

989
01:14:40,200 --> 01:14:43,300
<font color="#fefefe">-Sorry.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-You told them? I don't need credit.</font>

990
01:14:43,700 --> 01:14:45,300
<font color="#fefefe">I didn't tell anybody.</font>

991
01:14:45,600 --> 01:14:47,500
<font color="#fefefe">And I wasn't giving you the credit.</font>

992
01:14:47,800 --> 01:14:49,500
<font color="#fefefe">I'll finish. They'll never know.</font>

993
01:14:49,800 --> 01:14:52,400
<font color="#fefefe">I'm sick about it. But they'll know.</font>

994
01:14:52,700 --> 01:14:54,600
<font color="#fefefe">NORMAN: All right, gather around.</font>

995
01:14:55,100 --> 01:14:56,500
<font color="#fefefe">Wait a minute.</font>

996
01:14:56,900 --> 01:14:59,300
<font color="#fefefe">I don't want a new director every hour.</font>

997
01:14:59,700 --> 01:15:03,200
<font color="#fefefe">Who the fuck gave you a vote?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Don't tell me who to hire.</font>

998
01:15:03,600 --> 01:15:07,700
<font color="#fefefe">Fire him and I walk. Junk this shit.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Explain that to your money man.</font>

999
01:15:08,100 --> 01:15:09,800
<font color="#fefefe">Tell him how cold it is out there.</font>

1000
01:15:10,200 --> 01:15:12,500
<font color="#fefefe">You want to share his coffin? Tell him.</font>

1001
01:15:12,800 --> 01:15:14,300
<font color="#fefefe">You end up working for assholes.</font>

1002
01:15:14,500 --> 01:15:17,300
<font color="#fefefe">Nice. This asshole just fired you.</font>

1003
01:15:17,800 --> 01:15:19,700
<font color="#fefefe">Shitkicker, come back here.</font>

1004
01:15:20,100 --> 01:15:21,800
<i><font color="#fefefe">I'm talking to you, Commie!</font></i>

1005
01:15:22,700 --> 01:15:26,100
<font color="#fefefe">No one calls me a Commie,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">you son of a bitch!</font>

1006
01:15:26,500 --> 01:15:29,400
<font color="#fefefe">I volunteered names of Communists I knew.</font>

1007
01:15:29,900 --> 01:15:31,800
<font color="#fefefe">You call me a Commie? Back it up!</font>

1008
01:15:32,100 --> 01:15:35,300
<font color="#fefefe">If he calls you a Commie,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">he doesn't have to back it up.</font>

1009
01:15:35,600 --> 01:15:37,100
<font color="#fefefe">Get the shot list.</font>

1010
01:15:37,400 --> 01:15:39,900
<font color="#fefefe">Sorry about this. I need the job.</font>

1011
01:15:40,300 --> 01:15:42,500
<font color="#fefefe">Take care of him. Life's not a cowboy movie.</font>

1012
01:15:42,800 --> 01:15:46,700
<font color="#fefefe">GENE: Don't worry.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I'll be in my office if you need anything.</font>

1013
01:15:47,200 --> 01:15:51,700
<font color="#fefefe">We'll go down the aisle together.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">We're going to the Oscars.</font>

1014
01:16:08,000 --> 01:16:08,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Funny.</font>

1015
01:16:10,000 --> 01:16:11,200
<font color="#fefefe">Seen enough?</font>

1016
01:16:12,400 --> 01:16:14,200
<font color="#fefefe">He's got funny hair.</font>

1017
01:16:22,100 --> 01:16:24,100
<font color="#fefefe">Come on, Paulie, let's go.</font>

1018
01:16:28,900 --> 01:16:30,600
<font color="#fefefe">PAULIE: Isn't it neat?</font>

1019
01:16:31,800 --> 01:16:33,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">It's like Stevie's.</font></i>

1020
01:16:34,100 --> 01:16:36,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">It's too big for me.</font></i>

1021
01:16:36,700 --> 01:16:38,600
<font color="#fefefe">Stay here. Stay right here.</font>

1022
01:16:39,800 --> 01:16:43,400
<font color="#fefefe">-What's wrong with you? It's Christmas!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-You got a problem?</font>

1023
01:16:43,800 --> 01:16:45,100
<font color="#fefefe">Goddamn right!</font>

1024
01:16:49,000 --> 01:16:51,400
<font color="#fefefe">-Stop it! What's wrong?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">-I don't know.</font>

1025
01:16:52,600 --> 01:16:55,800
<font color="#fefefe">I'm sorry. I thought you were someone else.</font>

1026
01:16:56,300 --> 01:16:58,200
<font color="#fefefe">Merry Christmas, pal.</font>

1027
01:16:59,300 --> 01:17:00,800
<font color="#fefefe">I thought you were someone else.</font>

1028
01:17:04,200 --> 01:17:05,700
<font color="#fefefe">[Festive singing]</font>

1029
01:17:05,800 --> 01:17:07,700
<font color="#fefefe">I'm looking for Felix Graff.</font>

1030
01:17:12,500 --> 01:17:14,200
<font color="#fefefe">David, come in.</font>

1031
01:17:14,600 --> 01:17:16,300
<font color="#fefefe">Some mob out there.</font>

1032
01:17:16,600 --> 01:17:18,200
<font color="#fefefe">Can I get you a drink?</font>

1033
01:17:18,500 --> 01:17:19,600
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: No, thanks.</font>

1034
01:17:20,000 --> 01:17:21,700
<font color="#fefefe">You've lost some weight.</font>

1035
01:17:23,300 --> 01:17:25,200
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: I wish I could lose some.</font>

1036
01:17:25,900 --> 01:17:28,400
<font color="#fefefe">It's all this damn Christmas cheer.</font>

1037
01:17:29,500 --> 01:17:31,000
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: Hors d'oeuvre?</font>

1038
01:17:34,800 --> 01:17:36,100
<font color="#fefefe">How you doing?</font>

1039
01:17:37,900 --> 01:17:39,800
<font color="#fefefe">It's good news you're here.</font>

1040
01:17:40,600 --> 01:17:44,800
<font color="#fefefe">I presume you had a chance to think</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and put things in perspective.</font>

1041
01:17:47,400 --> 01:17:49,600
<font color="#fefefe">I know this is difficult, David.</font>

1042
01:17:50,000 --> 01:17:51,900
<font color="#fefefe">Nobody says it's easy.</font>

1043
01:17:52,400 --> 01:17:54,400
<font color="#fefefe">But you've made the right decision.</font>

1044
01:17:56,300 --> 01:17:58,500
<font color="#fefefe">I haven't made any decision yet.</font>

1045
01:18:05,400 --> 01:18:09,700
<font color="#fefefe">Isn't there anything I can do?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Like the American Civil Liberties Union?</font>

1046
01:18:10,100 --> 01:18:11,400
<font color="#fefefe">Can I take the Fifth?</font>

1047
01:18:11,700 --> 01:18:14,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID:</font>
<font color="#fefefe">They can't do anything to me then, right?</font>

1048
01:18:14,600 --> 01:18:18,600
<font color="#fefefe">Not a real alternative.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">It implies that you're hiding something.</font>

1049
01:18:19,100 --> 01:18:23,400
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: The only thing to hide, they think,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">is Communist Party membership.</font>

1050
01:18:24,200 --> 01:18:27,400
<font color="#fefefe">You protect yourself against</font>
<font color="#fefefe">self-incrimination but...</font>

1051
01:18:27,800 --> 01:18:31,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">...you're guilty by suspicion.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Where does that get you?</font></i>

1052
01:18:34,500 --> 01:18:37,200
<font color="#fefefe">You asked how I'm doing.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">You want to know?</font>

1053
01:18:39,200 --> 01:18:40,700
<font color="#fefefe">I can't get a job.</font>

1054
01:18:41,800 --> 01:18:43,200
<font color="#fefefe">Can't get a job.</font>

1055
01:18:44,900 --> 01:18:47,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: All my friends gone.</font>

1056
01:18:49,300 --> 01:18:53,500
<font color="#fefefe">I'm followed by the FBI. I lost my house.</font>

1057
01:18:54,200 --> 01:18:57,100
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID:</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I can't even buy my son a bike for Christmas.</font>

1058
01:18:58,000 --> 01:19:00,800
<font color="#fefefe">Is it worth all this pain, David?</font>

1059
01:19:02,400 --> 01:19:06,000
<font color="#fefefe">Is it worth it to your little boy, for example?</font>

1060
01:19:06,400 --> 01:19:09,100
<font color="#fefefe">What about Dorothy's little boy?</font>

1061
01:19:09,600 --> 01:19:12,400
<font color="#fefefe">That 6-year-old little boy lost his mother.</font>

1062
01:19:12,600 --> 01:19:14,200
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: That's what I'm saying.</font>

1063
01:19:14,500 --> 01:19:16,200
<font color="#fefefe">Is it worth all this?</font>

1064
01:19:17,800 --> 01:19:19,700
<font color="#fefefe">What are they asking you to do?</font>

1065
01:19:20,100 --> 01:19:23,900
<font color="#fefefe">Just say, ''I'm sorry. I was young and foolish.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I made a mistake.</font>

1066
01:19:24,400 --> 01:19:26,000
<font color="#fefefe">''I was immature.''</font>

1067
01:19:26,400 --> 01:19:27,900
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: That isn't much.</font>

1068
01:19:29,800 --> 01:19:32,300
<font color="#fefefe">I'm being asked to do more than that.</font>

1069
01:19:35,100 --> 01:19:38,600
<font color="#fefefe">A lot of people in this country</font>
<font color="#fefefe">as smart as you...</font>

1070
01:19:38,900 --> 01:19:40,800
<font color="#fefefe">...think the Committee's good.</font>

1071
01:19:41,000 --> 01:19:42,500
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: A lot of people.</font>

1072
01:19:51,300 --> 01:19:54,200
<font color="#fefefe">So, when will I get the subpoena?</font>

1073
01:19:54,700 --> 01:19:56,600
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: Two weeks, maybe three.</font>

1074
01:19:58,100 --> 01:20:00,400
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: You're not Cooper or Gable.</font>

1075
01:20:00,700 --> 01:20:05,300
<font color="#fefefe">You're David. I'm Felix.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">We have wives and kids and doctors' bills.</font>

1076
01:20:05,800 --> 01:20:08,300
<font color="#fefefe">This isn't some big screen drama.</font>

1077
01:20:08,700 --> 01:20:10,200
<font color="#fefefe">Think of yourself.</font>

1078
01:20:10,600 --> 01:20:13,300
<font color="#fefefe">Don't confuse it with one of your movies.</font>

1079
01:20:13,600 --> 01:20:17,800
<font color="#fefefe">GRAFF: Ever seen Cooper on screen having</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to open a doctor's bill?</font>

1080
01:20:49,600 --> 01:20:50,900
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: Why are you here?</font>

1081
01:20:52,300 --> 01:20:53,800
<font color="#fefefe">You look like shit.</font>

1082
01:20:56,100 --> 01:20:57,400
<font color="#fefefe">Come in.</font>

1083
01:21:00,000 --> 01:21:01,500
<font color="#fefefe">You were right.</font>

1084
01:21:02,200 --> 01:21:03,800
<font color="#fefefe">I should have called a lawyer.</font>

1085
01:21:05,200 --> 01:21:06,700
<font color="#fefefe">But I didn't.</font>

1086
01:21:07,300 --> 01:21:10,100
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: So I went down</font>
<font color="#fefefe">just to clear my name.</font>

1087
01:21:12,300 --> 01:21:14,500
<font color="#fefefe">To say I was never a Party member.</font>

1088
01:21:14,800 --> 01:21:18,200
<font color="#fefefe">They said, ''Fine.'' I said, ''Can I go now?''</font>

1089
01:21:18,600 --> 01:21:22,000
<font color="#fefefe">They said,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">''After you sign a sworn statement.''</font>

1090
01:21:22,500 --> 01:21:23,800
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: I said, ''Fine.''</font>

1091
01:21:24,400 --> 01:21:26,300
<font color="#fefefe">But in New York...</font>

1092
01:21:27,500 --> 01:21:29,100
<font color="#fefefe">...so long ago...</font>

1093
01:21:30,100 --> 01:21:32,100
<font color="#fefefe">...this girl, Magda...</font>

1094
01:21:33,800 --> 01:21:35,400
<font color="#fefefe">...took me to a meeting.</font>

1095
01:21:37,600 --> 01:21:40,900
<font color="#fefefe">They thought we could help the folks</font>
<font color="#fefefe">in Russia...</font>

1096
01:21:41,400 --> 01:21:44,000
<font color="#fefefe">...by sending canned goods and clothes.</font>

1097
01:21:45,800 --> 01:21:49,800
<font color="#fefefe">Russia was our ally.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">The Germans were attacking Stalingrad.</font>

1098
01:21:50,100 --> 01:21:52,300
<font color="#fefefe">We were both fighting the damn Nazis.</font>

1099
01:21:56,900 --> 01:21:58,500
<font color="#fefefe">This meeting was just...</font>

1100
01:21:59,000 --> 01:22:01,500
<font color="#fefefe">...people caring about people.</font>

1101
01:22:05,300 --> 01:22:06,800
