<font color="#fefefe">meeting at your home last September 21?</font>

1278
01:36:10,200 --> 01:36:12,400
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: I don't know</font>
<font color="#fefefe">what you're talking about.</font>

1279
01:36:12,800 --> 01:36:15,600
<font color="#fefefe">VELDE: Tell me if the following people</font>
<font color="#fefefe">were present:</font>

1280
01:36:16,100 --> 01:36:20,600
<font color="#fefefe">VELDE: ''Dorothy Nolan, Joe Lesser,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Nelly Lesser, Claude Rowan, Bert Alan.''</font>

1281
01:36:21,100 --> 01:36:25,500
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: When I returned from France, my</font>
<font color="#fefefe">friends threw a surprise party at my house.</font>

1282
01:36:26,000 --> 01:36:29,200
<font color="#fefefe">If I tell you who was there,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">everyone would be a Communist! I refuse.</font>

1283
01:36:29,700 --> 01:36:31,100
<font color="#fefefe">I won't do that.</font>

1284
01:36:31,300 --> 01:36:33,700
<font color="#fefefe">I remind this Committee and you...</font>

1285
01:36:34,100 --> 01:36:36,900
<font color="#fefefe">...of the sworn testimony from Larry Nolan...</font>

1286
01:36:37,300 --> 01:36:38,900
<i><font color="#fefefe">...that David Merrill--</font></i>

1287
01:36:39,100 --> 01:36:42,000
<font color="#fefefe">Did Larry Nolan testify</font>
<font color="#fefefe">that he burned books...</font>

1288
01:36:42,400 --> 01:36:45,500
<font color="#fefefe">...because he was afraid to be caught</font>
<font color="#fefefe">with those books?</font>

1289
01:36:45,900 --> 01:36:50,100
<font color="#fefefe">Some books should be burned!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Libraries are full of Communist filth!</font>

1290
01:36:50,600 --> 01:36:53,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">Alice in Wonderland? Huckleberry Finn?</font></i>

1291
01:36:55,100 --> 01:36:56,900
<font color="#fefefe">How many Communists do you know?</font>

1292
01:36:57,200 --> 01:36:59,400
<i><font color="#fefefe">How many have you worked with?</font></i>

1293
01:36:59,800 --> 01:37:02,200
<i><font color="#fefefe">What is your association with them?</font></i>

1294
01:37:02,500 --> 01:37:05,500
<font color="#fefefe">What are their names? A simple question.</font>

1295
01:37:05,800 --> 01:37:07,800
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Will the Congressman yield?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">VELDE: Yes.</font>

1296
01:37:07,900 --> 01:37:09,600
<font color="#fefefe">Is Ruth Merrill...</font>

1297
01:37:09,900 --> 01:37:12,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">...a member of the Communist Party?</font></i>

1298
01:37:12,300 --> 01:37:15,300
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: My wife?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: You mean your ex-wife?</font>

1299
01:37:15,800 --> 01:37:19,700
<font color="#fefefe">Here she is at the ''Ban the Bomb'' bash</font>
<font color="#fefefe">that you all threw.</font>

1300
01:37:20,500 --> 01:37:23,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">Clearly mocking our government.</font></i>

1301
01:37:23,400 --> 01:37:27,500
<font color="#fefefe">Should a person like this be allowed</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to teach impressionable children?</font>

1302
01:37:28,100 --> 01:37:32,200
<font color="#fefefe">Children have the right to discuss</font>
<font color="#fefefe">government in school.</font>

1303
01:37:32,600 --> 01:37:34,900
<font color="#fefefe">She must be barred from influencing</font>
<font color="#fefefe">young minds.</font>

1304
01:37:35,300 --> 01:37:39,300
<font color="#fefefe">And I will see to it</font>
<font color="#fefefe">that legislation is adopted...</font>

1305
01:37:39,600 --> 01:37:42,300
<font color="#fefefe">...requiring teachers to take a loyalty oath.</font>

1306
01:37:42,700 --> 01:37:45,400
<font color="#fefefe">To prevent people like her from teaching!</font>

1307
01:37:45,700 --> 01:37:47,700
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: She doesn't want them killed</font>
<font color="#fefefe">by atomic bombs!</font>

1308
01:37:48,500 --> 01:37:50,000
<font color="#fefefe">She's disloyal!</font>

1309
01:37:50,300 --> 01:37:52,500
<font color="#fefefe">By teaching respect for the Constitution?</font>

1310
01:37:52,800 --> 01:37:56,700
<font color="#fefefe">Is Ruth Merrill now or has she ever been</font>
<font color="#fefefe">a Communist? Yes or no?</font>

1311
01:37:57,100 --> 01:38:00,400
<font color="#fefefe">No. Never. Absolutely, categorically, no.</font>

1312
01:38:01,200 --> 01:38:02,800
<font color="#fefefe">What about Dorothy Nolan?</font>

1313
01:38:03,200 --> 01:38:05,700
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Was she ever a Communist?</font>
<font color="#fefefe">DAVID: She's dead.</font>

1314
01:38:06,000 --> 01:38:07,700
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: That's not what I asked.</font>

1315
01:38:08,000 --> 01:38:10,500
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Now answer these questions.</font>

1316
01:38:10,800 --> 01:38:14,300
<font color="#fefefe">Was Dorothy Nolan a Communist? Yes or no?</font>

1317
01:38:14,600 --> 01:38:16,400
<font color="#fefefe">Don't you have any decency?</font>

1318
01:38:16,700 --> 01:38:18,100
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Unfortunately...</font>

1319
01:38:18,500 --> 01:38:22,300
<font color="#fefefe">...Dorothy Nolan was a known drunk,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">an unfit parent...</font>

1320
01:38:22,800 --> 01:38:25,900
<i><font color="#fefefe">...and had been named as a Communist.</font></i>

1321
01:38:26,300 --> 01:38:29,600
<font color="#fefefe">She was a good mother.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">You're responsible for her death!</font>

1322
01:38:29,900 --> 01:38:32,300
<font color="#fefefe">She has been named as a Communist!</font>

1323
01:38:32,500 --> 01:38:35,200
<font color="#fefefe">She was falsely accused.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">She was out of work.</font>

1324
01:38:35,500 --> 01:38:37,900
<font color="#fefefe">She lost her son because of this Committee!</font>

1325
01:38:38,200 --> 01:38:41,500
<font color="#fefefe">She killed herself.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">The Communists twisted her mind.</font>

1326
01:38:42,000 --> 01:38:45,900
<font color="#fefefe">In the name of ridding the world</font>
<font color="#fefefe">of Communism, you destroyed her!</font>

1327
01:38:46,300 --> 01:38:48,800
<font color="#fefefe">Have you no shame? She's dead!</font>

1328
01:38:49,100 --> 01:38:51,000
<font color="#fefefe">I'm tired of acting...</font>

1329
01:38:51,300 --> 01:38:53,600
<font color="#fefefe">...as though we're playing some little game!</font>

1330
01:38:53,900 --> 01:38:55,900
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: This Committee</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and its activities...</font>

1331
01:38:56,400 --> 01:39:00,200
<font color="#fefefe">...may very well determine the future</font>
<font color="#fefefe">of this great country!</font>

1332
01:39:00,600 --> 01:39:04,200
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: One Communist in America is</font>
<font color="#fefefe">one too many, I say!</font>

1333
01:39:04,600 --> 01:39:06,800
<i><font color="#fefefe">You don't care about this country.</font></i>

1334
01:39:07,100 --> 01:39:10,800
<font color="#fefefe">No concern for the damage you</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and your Communist friends...</font>

1335
01:39:11,200 --> 01:39:15,600
<font color="#fefefe">...have inflicted on the minds</font>
<font color="#fefefe">of free Americans with your films and TV.</font>

1336
01:39:16,300 --> 01:39:19,500
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Sir, your refusal to answer</font>
<font color="#fefefe">our questions...</font>

1337
01:39:20,000 --> 01:39:23,800
<font color="#fefefe">...means you are still a member</font>
<font color="#fefefe">of the Communist Party...</font>

1338
01:39:24,200 --> 01:39:25,800
<font color="#fefefe">...and a threat to us all!</font>

1339
01:39:27,300 --> 01:39:28,700
<font color="#fefefe">Next witness!</font>

1340
01:39:29,000 --> 01:39:31,500
<font color="#fefefe">VELDE: I move that this witness be cited</font>
<font color="#fefefe">for contempt!</font>

1341
01:39:31,900 --> 01:39:33,500
<font color="#fefefe">I might not be the--</font>

1342
01:39:33,800 --> 01:39:35,400
<font color="#fefefe">You had your chance to speak!</font>

1343
01:39:35,700 --> 01:39:39,800
<font color="#fefefe">I was raised to stand up for my beliefs</font>
<font color="#fefefe">and I'll raise my son the same way!</font>

1344
01:39:40,300 --> 01:39:42,600
<font color="#fefefe">And I'm going to try to live it!</font>

1345
01:39:43,000 --> 01:39:47,700
<font color="#fefefe">If that isn't what a real American is,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">then we've failed! Shame on you!</font>

1346
01:39:48,100 --> 01:39:49,800
<font color="#fefefe">You're dismissed! Remove him!</font>

1347
01:39:50,500 --> 01:39:53,200
<font color="#fefefe">VELDE: A real American would be proud</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to answer.</font>

1348
01:39:53,400 --> 01:39:54,600
<font color="#fefefe">Shame on you!</font>

1349
01:39:57,400 --> 01:39:58,800
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Next witness!</font>

1350
01:40:03,000 --> 01:40:04,600
<font color="#fefefe">RUTH: There's Bunny.</font>

1351
01:40:06,000 --> 01:40:07,200
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Quiet!</font>

1352
01:40:10,200 --> 01:40:12,300
<i><font color="#fefefe">This hearing will come to order.</font></i>

1353
01:40:12,600 --> 01:40:14,000
<i><font color="#fefefe">Hold up your right hand.</font></i>

1354
01:40:14,300 --> 01:40:17,000
<font color="#fefefe">You do solemnly swear the evidence</font>
<font color="#fefefe">you are going to give...</font>

1355
01:40:17,200 --> 01:40:20,100
<font color="#fefefe">...will be the truth, and nothing but the truth,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">so help you God?</font>

1356
01:40:20,300 --> 01:40:21,600
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Yes.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Be seated.</font>

1357
01:40:23,700 --> 01:40:26,000
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: Your profession is</font>
<font color="#fefefe">as a screenwriter?</font>

1358
01:40:26,200 --> 01:40:27,800
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Yes.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: Were you subpoenaed?</font>

1359
01:40:27,900 --> 01:40:29,700
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: Yes.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">TAVENNER: I'd like to begin...</font>

1360
01:40:29,900 --> 01:40:32,100
<i><font color="#fefefe">...if you don't mind,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">by clearing this matter up.</font></i>

1361
01:40:32,300 --> 01:40:35,600
<i><font color="#fefefe">Are you now, or have you ever been,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">a member of the Communist party?</font></i>

1362
01:40:40,600 --> 01:40:41,500
<font color="#fefefe">Mr. Chairman...</font>

1363
01:40:42,700 --> 01:40:46,400
<font color="#fefefe">...regardless of consequence to myself,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">I must refuse to answer that question...</font>

1364
01:40:46,800 --> 01:40:49,400
<font color="#fefefe">...for many reasons.</font>
<font color="#fefefe">Primarily, it violates my right...</font>

1365
01:40:49,500 --> 01:40:51,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">...from the First Amendment</font>
<font color="#fefefe">to the Constitution.</font></i>

1366
01:40:52,200 --> 01:40:54,300
<i><font color="#fefefe">We all have a right to the freedom of speech.</font></i>

1367
01:40:55,600 --> 01:40:57,400
<i><font color="#fefefe">Freedom of speech! Freedom of assembly.</font></i>

1368
01:40:57,500 --> 01:41:00,300
<font color="#fefefe">CHAIRMAN: Answer the question!</font>
<font color="#fefefe">BUNNY: I am trying to answer...</font>

1369
01:41:00,500 --> 01:41:03,300
<i><font color="#fefefe">...but under the circumstances,</font>
<font color="#fefefe">it appears I must use...</font></i>

1370
01:41:03,500 --> 01:41:06,500
<i><font color="#fefefe">...my Constitutional right</font>
<font color="#fefefe">as an American citizen.</font></i>

1371
01:41:47,500 --> 01:41:49,800
<font color="#fefefe">[Sorrowful instrumental music]</font>

1372
01:42:52,400 --> 01:42:55,000
<font color="#fefefe">[Soft instrumental jazz]</font>

